modName: Hidden Vale Trees and only white grass For SoSP Winter
summary:
This replaces all trees with the ones found in Dawnguard Vale.
<br />It also removes the straw-coloured grass and replaces it with the ice white variant.
descriptionHtml:
This replaces all trees with the ones found in Dawnguard Vale.
<br />It also removes the straw-coloured grass and replaces it with the ice white variant.
<br />
<br />Obviously you need SoSP Winter for this to work but it does not directly use any elements from SoSP Winter Edition.
<br />
<br />The black Orc skin was made by me, if enough people want it, I'll add it.
author: Millionade
